1. Set Up Your Project:
-->npx create-next-app@latest gas-tracker --typescript
-->cd gas-tracker
Choose the following when prompted:

✔ TypeScript: Yes

✔ App Router: Yes

✔ Tailwind: Optional (not required)

✔ ESLint: Yes (optional)


2. Run the App
-->npm run dev
Open your browser and go to: http://localhost:3000

You should see:

A candlestick chart of Ethereum gas fees (live)

Input field to simulate a transaction

USD cost calculation
